data.title: Festival Express Collectable Lanyard
data.meta_description: Festival Express Collectable Lanyard - Entertainment Venues
data.text:
Festival Express 10 Day Pass Collectable Lanyard - available at the Bus Ticket Booth

If you want to have the full festival experience then travelling on the Festival Express is THE BEST way for you to see not just the festival activities but also Tamworth itself.

Tamworth Country Music Festival is like no other with 10 full days of music and events featuring ticketed and free shows accross the entire city from pub to park and club to entertainment centre.

Staying outside the CBD and want to easily get into the free park events and other activities? Or, staying in the CBD and want to see the other amazing attractions and venues that Tamworth and surrounds have to offer? Then this is the travel pass for you.

Wear it around your neck, attach it to your bag or slip it in your pocket, this collectable is a ticket to ride!

In 2024 you can purchase a Festival Express Collectable Lanyard that is your 10 day unlimited bus pass. The 10 day pass gives you unlimited travel on the Festival Express bus service that has stops all over town. With this pass you can get on and off at any stop you wish, all day and into the evening.

And at the conclusion of festival you have a momento to remind you of the amazing time you had at the Tamworth Country Music Festival in 2024.

Collectable Lanyards are limited so if you think you'd like to experience all that Tamworth can offer pre purchase yours today.

What you receive: One collectable FESTIVAL EXPRESS 10 day bus pass and lanyard + One plastic protective sleeve
